metadata.name: Zenlicious#1
metadata.description: Zenlicious is the first-ever food video to pioneer in the NFT space. While promoting Chinese food culture, it also hopes to convey to the World the traditional Chinese aesthetic values and how Zen provides a holistic view of the unity of man and nature. The whole NFT collection not only takes into account the desire for aesthetic needs of both the Eastern and the Western cultures, but is also a milestone taken by the NFT Aerfa community to expand to the English-speaking market.
